# Workflow Discipline

• PLAN_BEFORE_ACT — For any change touching >50 LOC or >1 file, Cursor must enter # Mode: PLAN, list affected files, and await approval.

• SMALL_COMMITS — Each ACT chunk ≤ 50 LOC unless user explicitly waives.

• NO_CYCLIC_IMPORTS — If mypy or ruff detects a cycle, stop and propose a fix before continuing.

